# рџ”„ GitHub Actions Workflows

The automation system is modular and separated into independent workflows.

---

## 1пёЏвѓЈ Update Vault Status (Weekly)

* Scrapes Warframe Wiki
* Generates `vaultStatus.json`
* Commits only if changes exist
* Runs weekly via scheduled cron

---

## 2пёЏвѓЈ Update Relics + Prices (On Vault Change)

Triggered when:

* Vault status changes
  OR
* Manually dispatched

Generates:

* `Relics.min.json`
* `prices.json`

Commits only if data changed.

---

## 3пёЏвѓЈ Vault Safety Re-Check

* Validates Wiki parsing
* Ensures mapping integrity
* Prevents incorrect deployments

Acts as a guard layer between data generation and deployment.

---

## 4пёЏвѓЈ Deploy UI

* Deploys static site to GitHub Pages
* Triggered on:

  * Push to main
  * Workflow completion
  * Manual dispatch

No hosting server required.

